headline: Kinder Morgan Adds Another $1.4 Billion Project to Fuel Its More Than 4%-Yielding Dividend
summary: Kinder Morgan (NYSE: KMI) pays its investors well.  The pipeline company should have plenty of fuel to keep growing its dividends in the coming years.  One factor powering that view is its ability to secure needle-moving expansion projects.
